    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that 'new car' magic. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
