    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a peerless 1991 BMW M3 (E30) that defines concourse quality. This specimen features the legendary S14B23 dual-overhead-cam inline-four, breathing through factory-spec individual throttle bodies and mated to a precise Getrag 265 five-speed manual transmission. The mechanical synchronization is flawless, with the limited-slip differential providing optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. The suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the communicative handling these chassis are known for. Body panels are laser-straight with all factory VIN tags intact, and the paint depth is consistent throughout. The interior is an exercise in preservation, featuring pristine upholstery and a crack-free dashboard. A mechanically superlative example for the serious collector.",
      "price": 43500.0,
