      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, retaining its original showroom luster with zero chips, swirls, or imperfections in the deep metallic paint. The interior is equally breathtaking; the premium leather remains supple with no creasing, and the cabin still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule by factory-certified technicians, backed by a comprehensive folder of maintenance records. From the flawless alloy wheels to the pristine, untouched undercarriage, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. It comes complete with all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover. For the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality icon.",
